<plot>A group of indolent bonvivants stage an accident in order to cadge money for alcohol. The scheme backfires when one of the conspirators is simply too lazy to fulfill his particular function. The others have little time to regret their brief bursts of enterprise, as, in a delightful pixelated sequence, they are flattened by a passing coal truck.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?361570</url></doc>
